import {NavLink, Outlet} from 'react-router-dom';

import Main from '../layouts/main'
import Subnavigation from '../layouts/subnavigation'
import SubnavItem from '../layouts/subnavitem'
import '../styles/theme.css'

const Issues = ({className}) => (
  <Main className={className}>
    <Subnavigation title='Issues'>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/'>All</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/issues/saved1'>View1</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/issues/saved2'>View2</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
    </Subnavigation>
    <Outlet/>
  </Main>
);

export default Issues;
